## 3. Architecture

### 3.1 System Overview

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   Job Sources                        │
│  ┌──────────┐  ┌───────────┐  ┌──────────────┐     │
│  │  Indeed   │  │ LinkedIn  │  │  StepStone   │     │
│  │ (JSearch) │  │ (SerpAPI) │  │ (SerpAPI +   │     │
│  │          │  │           │  │  Direct)     │     │
│  └────┬─────┘  └─────┬─────┘  └──────┬───────┘     │
└───────┼──────────────┼───────────────┼──────────────┘
        │              │               │
        ▼              ▼               ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│          Vercel Cron Job (every 4 hours)             │
│          POST /api/jobs/cron                         │
│          ┌──────────────────────┐                    │
│          │   Profile Matcher    │                    │
│          │   (score 0-100)      │                    │
│          └──────────┬───────────┘                    │
└─────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────┘
                      │
                      ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              Supabase (PostgreSQL)                    │
│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌─────────────────┐              │
│  │  jobs table   │  │  cron_logs table │              │
│  └──────────────┘  └─────────────────┘              │
└─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                      │
                      ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│         anilkhanna.dev/jobs (Dashboard)               │
│  ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌───────────────┐       │
│  │  Stats   │ │ Job List │ │ Detail Panel  │       │
│  │  Bar     │ │ (cards)  │ │ (actions)     │       │
│  └──────────┘ └──────────┘ └───────────────┘       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### 3.2 Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Reason |
|-------|-----------|--------|
| Frontend | Next.js 15, React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS | Existing portfolio stack |
| Backend | Next.js API Routes (serverless) | Same codebase, zero infra |
| Database | Supabase (PostgreSQL, free tier) | Full SQL, 500MB free, existing project |
| Scheduler | Vercel Cron | Built-in, free on Hobby plan |
| Job APIs | RapidAPI JSearch + SerpAPI | Free tiers, broad coverage |
| Auth | Cookie-based with `admin_password` env | Reuses existing admin auth |
| Deployment | Vercel (auto-deploy from GitHub) | Existing CI/CD pipeline |

### 3.3 Database Schema

**Table: `jobs`**

| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `id` | UUID (PK) | Auto-generated |
| `external_id` | TEXT | Platform-specific job ID |
| `platform` | TEXT | `indeed`, `linkedin`, `stepstone` |
| `title` | TEXT | Job title |
| `company` | TEXT | Company name |
| `location` | TEXT | Job location |
| `job_url` | TEXT | Direct link to apply |
| `description` | TEXT | Job description (truncated to 5000 chars) |
| `salary_range` | TEXT | Salary info if available |
| `job_type` | TEXT | `full-time`, `part-time`, `contract` |
| `work_mode` | TEXT | `remote`, `hybrid`, `onsite` |
| `match_score` | NUMERIC(5,2) | Profile match score (0-100) |
| `matched_skills` | TEXT[] | Skills that matched |
| `status` | TEXT | `new`, `reviewed`, `saved`, `applied`, `rejected`, `expired` |
| `notes` | TEXT | Personal notes |
| `posted_at` | TIMESTAMPTZ | When the job was posted |
| `discovered_at` | TIMESTAMPTZ | When we found it |
| `updated_at` | TIMESTAMPTZ | Auto-updated on changes |

**Unique constraint:** `(external_id, platform)` — prevents duplicate entries.

**Table: `cron_logs`**

| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `id` | UUID (PK) | Auto-generated |
| `ran_at` | TIMESTAMPTZ | When the cron ran |
| `jobs_found` | INTEGER | Total raw jobs fetched |
| `jobs_new` | INTEGER | New jobs inserted |
| `jobs_updated` | INTEGER | Existing jobs updated |
| `errors` | TEXT[] | Error messages from fetchers |
| `duration_ms` | INTEGER | Total execution time |
| `status` | TEXT | `success`, `partial`, `failed` |

