## 6. Environment Variables

| Variable | Required | Source | Notes |
|----------|----------|--------|-------|
| `admin_password` | Yes | Existing | Already in Vercel env |
| `SUPABASE_URL` | Yes | Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API | Reuse existing: `https://gddixepkakojiuapcvbr.supabase.co` |
| `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` | Yes | Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API | Secret key (never expose publicly) |
| `CRON_SECRET` | Yes | Generate with `openssl rand -hex 32` | Protects cron endpoint |
| `RAPIDAPI_KEY` | Optional | [RapidAPI JSearch](https://rapidapi.com/letscrape-6bRBa3QguO5/api/jsearch) | For Indeed jobs |
| `SERPAPI_KEY` | Optional | [SerpAPI](https://serpapi.com) | For LinkedIn + StepStone |

At least one of `RAPIDAPI_KEY` or `SERPAPI_KEY` is recommended.

