## 11. Security Considerations

- Dashboard is password-protected (reuses `admin_password`)
- Page has `robots: { index: false, follow: false }` meta tags
- Supabase uses service role key (server-side only, never exposed to client)
- Cron endpoint is protected by `CRON_SECRET` bearer token
- HTTP-only cookies prevent XSS token theft
- Row Level Security enabled on Supabase tables
- No sensitive data stored in the repo (all env variables)

---

