## 13. Success Metrics

| Metric | Target |
|--------|--------|
| Jobs discovered per day | 20-50 |
| Match score accuracy (relevant jobs ≥50%) | >70% |
| Time saved vs manual search | 2+ hours/week |
| Dashboard load time | <2 seconds |
| Cron execution time | <30 seconds |
| Zero recurring cost | All free tiers |

---

## 14. Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|-----------|
| API rate limits exceeded | Missed job listings | Reduce queries per run, stagger fetchers |
| StepStone blocks scraping | Lose one source | SerpAPI fallback, respect rate limits |
| Supabase free tier fills up | Database full | Periodically archive old rejected/expired jobs |
| Job URLs expire | Broken "Apply" links | Mark as expired during next cron run |
| False positive matches | Noise in dashboard | Tune matcher weights, add negative keywords |
| Vercel cold starts | Slow cron execution | `maxDuration: 60` config, parallel fetching |